(106, 32, 'short_description', '<p>Finding the right handyman in Sydney could be tedious and costly, but Handy Oscar is your neighbourhood one-stop handyman service company guaranteed to offer quality products, innovative solutions, and excellent customer service! Let our growing list of satisfied clients and exceptional projects be a testament to the quality of our work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are a collective of passionate people, skilled at a wide range of trade handworks for your every home requirement. We specialize in wide variety of exterior and interior repairs and maintenance works, from the complicated task of plumbing to something as simple as changing your electrical light fixtures. No matter how big or small the job is, we’ll gladly take care of it for you!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our personnel are cross-trained experts in trade skills as electronics, plumbing, masonry, metal and wood works, carpentry, and general maintenance and repair works. We guarantee that the quality of our outputs are always at par with industry standards, or even better.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our growing range of handyman services currently includes fabrication and welding service, flooring services, pest control services, painting services, carpentry services repairs and renovations, electrical services, plumbing services, and granny flats conversions and building.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We cater to all industrial, commercial, and residential needs throughout the Sydney region, with pricing depending on the complexity of the work required. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>What sets our handyman services apart from the rest of our competitors are our custom assessment and proficient quotation, strictly tailored to your needs and demands. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our team of expert assessors will gladly help you with the initial assessment and free estimates. All it takes is one quick survey!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whatever services you may require, talk to us today, and let Handy Oscar give you a hand!</p>\r\n'),
(107, 32, 'short_title', 'We know how to do the job right!'),
