(17, 1, '2015-10-13 03:07:58', '2015-10-13 03:07:58', '<strong>Q. What services does LS Handyman Servives offer?</strong>\r\n\r\nWe are a professional handyman service specialising in small to medium jobs around the home and office. We focused on delivering more than you expect.\r\n\r\n<strong>Q. How do I book an appointment, how soon are you available?</strong>\r\n\r\nYou can contact Luca, that’s me , on 0415 557 263, best sms during the day as my hands are usually busy. Or call anytime, if I am busy making customers happy just leave a message. Email works well too. I will get back to you today.\r\n\r\n<strong>Q. Why use us ?</strong>\r\n\r\nYou will be sure of a hassle free, reliable, quality job which is great value for your money.\r\n\r\n<strong>Q. What services does LS Handyman Servives offer?</strong>\r\n\r\nWe are a professional handyman service specialising in small to medium jobs around the home and office. We focused on delivering more than you expect.\r\n\r\n<strong>Q. How do I book an appointment, how soon are you available?</strong>\r\n\r\nYou can contact Luca, that’s me , on 0415 557 263, best sms during the day as my hands are usually busy. Or call anytime, if I am busy making customers happy just leave a message. Email works well too. I will get back to you today.\r\n\r\n<strong>Q. Why use us ?</strong>\r\n\r\nYou will be sure of a hassle free, reliable, quality job which is great value for your money.', 'FAQ''s', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'faqs', '', '', '2015-10-17 02:47:26', '2015-10-17 02:47:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/?page_id=17', 0, 'page', '', 0),
