(34, 1, '2015-10-13 04:21:39', '2015-10-13 04:21:39', '[text* your-name placeholder "Enter your name"]\r\n[email* your-email placeholder "Enter your email"]\r\n[tel* phone-number placeholder "Enter your phone"]\r\n[text* message placeholder "Message"]\r\n[submit class:common_form_submit "Submit"]\n[your-subject]\n[your-name] <adnin@gmail.com>\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n--\r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on Handy Oscar (http://localhost/wp-ultra)\nadnin@gmail.com\nReply-To: [your-email]\n\n\n\n\n[your-subject]\nHandy Oscar <adnin@gmail.com>\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n--\r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on Handy Oscar (http://localhost/wp-ultra)\n[your-email]\nReply-To: adnin@gmail.com\n\n\n\nYour message was sent successfully. Thanks.\nFailed to send your message. Please try later or contact the administrator by another method.\nValidation errors occurred.\nFailed to send your message. Please try later or contact the administrator by another method.\nPlease accept the terms to proceed.\nPlease fill in the required field.\nThis input is too long.\nThis input is too short.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nNumber format seems invalid.\nThis number is too small.\nThis number is too large.\nEmail address seems invalid.\nURL seems invalid.\nTelephone number seems invalid.\nYour answer is not correct.\nDate format seems invalid.\nThis date is too early.\nThis date is too late.\nFailed to upload file.\nThis file type is not allowed.\nThis file is too large.\nFailed to upload file. Error occurred.', 'Contact form 1', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'contact-form-1', '', '', '2015-10-15 03:49:21', '2015-10-15 03:49:21', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=34', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
(35, 1, '2015-10-15 04:10:56', '2015-10-15 04:10:56', '<h2>Want to build a robust iron gate for your fortress or just a simple fixing of loose structural parts? Our fabrication and welding services is the right choice for you!</h2>\r\nFabrication and welding are twin services that deal with metal works. The construction of metal structures such as gates, railings, or metal pipes usually comes in three folds: cutting, bending, and assembling processes.\r\n\r\nThese processes are often complicated, not to mention dangerous, so it’s not recommended for the technically-challenged and the faint-hearted. It also requires industry grade equipment that are usually not available in your neighbourhood do-it-yourself hardware.\r\n\r\nOur fabrication and welding services personnel are qualified &amp; experts in their fields and geared with all the right equipment for various metal works.\r\n\r\nOur fabrication and wielding services include material consultation and sourcing, structure designing and engineering, metal preparation and assembly, and project installation. It’s basically a one stop service that offers additional value and convenience for your metal needs.\r\nWe can work with different types of metals including, but not limited to wrought iron, brass, aluminium, and cast iron. From the complicated custom fabrication and joining multi-material structures, to simple repair of existing wields or joining plumbing pipes, Handy Oscar can give you a hand.\r\n\r\nWhen looking for a fabricator or welder, it is important to make sure that they have sufficient experience on the kind of job required, especially with the materials you prefer. There are strict rules on these types of services and require stringent protocols, assessments, and certifications. Other requirements include safety protective equipment and industry-standard tools.\r\n\r\nOur fabricators and welders are trained in compliance to these requirements. Our fabricators are equipped with years of experience working on different variety of materials and installation complexities, while our welders strictly adhere to international &amp; Australia Welding Procedure Specification (WPS) and Welder Certifications.\r\n<h3>So, contact or call 0457 895 033 if you’re looking for Fabrication and Welding services, let Handy Oscar give you a hand!</h3>', 'Fabrication & Welding Services', 'Our fabrication and wielding services include material consultation and sourcing, structure designing and engineering, metal preparation and assembly, and project installation. It’s basically a one stop service that offers additional value and convenience for your metal needs.\r\nWe can work with different types of metals including, but not limited to wrought iron, brass, aluminium, and cast iron', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'fabrication-welding-services', '', '', '2016-07-12 11:34:08', '2016-07-12 11:34:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/?post_type=services&#038;p=35', 0, 'services', '', 0),
(36, 1, '2015-10-15 04:12:45', '2015-10-15 04:12:45', '', 'home06', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'home06', '', '', '2015-10-15 04:12:45', '2015-10-15 04:12:45', '', 35, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/home06.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(37, 1, '2015-10-15 04:25:18', '2015-10-15 04:25:18', '<h2>Considering to change your household or office carpets? Do your tiled floors look a bit too out of date? Do your wooden floor boards need a little update? Our flooring services will tend to your every flooring needs.</h2>\r\nFlooring is a broad term for covering concrete floors, with materials divided into categories, such as soft coverings (carpets, rugs), wood floorings (plank, parquet), hard floorings (ceramic tiles, stone, terrazzo), resilient floorings (linoleum, vinyl), and seamless chemical floorings ( latex, polyester, urethane, epoxy) .\r\n\r\nWhile flooring jobs can range from the simple flat laying of area rugs, some flooring jobs like wood works require careful consideration. Some types of flooring, for instance, may not be installed below grade (lower than ground level), and laminate or hardwood should be avoided, where there may be moisture or condensation. The flooring process also takes into account the sub-floor, the structure where the flooring will be covered, and other factors as cost, endurance, comfort, and, of course, maintenance. While these tasks can surely be overwhelming, a friendly and expert Handyman is just what you’ll need.\r\n\r\nOur flooring personnel are expert installation craftsmen who are not only knowledgeable on the latest flooring materials and technology, but also up to date with the latest trends. Whether it be a basic ceramic tile or floor-to-wall carpets, our experts will make sure that everything, from the material, installation, and service, at-par with strict industry standards\r\n\r\nOur flooring services always start with site inspection and followed by technical recommendation of feasible flooring options. We both cater to residential, commercial flooring needs, which generally include carpets, woods, tiles, and chemical compounds.\r\n\r\nWe bank on the quality of our work, so we impose stringent quality assurance protocols to ensure that we only provide you the best flooring solutions and repair service with quality materials, all at very reasonable rates.\r\n<h3>So, contact us or call 0457 895 033 if you’re looking for flooring service &amp; repairs, let Handy Oscar give you a hand!</h3>', 'Flooring Services', 'Our flooring personnel are expert installation craftsmen who are not only knowledgeable on the latest flooring materials and technology, but also up to date with the latest trends. Whether it be a basic ceramic tile or floor-to-wall carpets, our experts will make sure that everything, from the material, installation, and service, at-par with strict industry standards', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'flooring-services', '', '', '2015-11-16 12:25:17', '2015-11-16 12:25:17', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/?post_type=services&#038;p=37', 0, 'services', '', 0),
(38, 1, '2015-10-15 04:25:13', '2015-10-15 04:25:13', '', 'home05', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'home05', '', '', '2015-10-15 04:25:13', '2015-10-15 04:25:13', '', 37, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/home05.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(39, 1, '2015-10-15 04:26:53', '2015-10-15 04:26:53', '<h2>Is your flat or house plagued by disgusting cockroaches? Are your beddings infested by annoying bed bugs? Are spiders getting too wearisome to handle? Pest buster Handy Oscar is here to the rescue.</h2>\r\nPest control requires proper management and regulation of pests that seemed to have evolved and increased their resistance to biological, chemical, and physical forms of control. Current pest control services are aimed at total extermination, through incapacitating these pests from reproduction.\r\n\r\nWhile precautionary measures, such as proper waste disposal and effective sewage management, may eliminate breeding grounds for many pests, some infestations come to a point where even physical traps, poisoned baits, and over-the-counter pesticides do not produce the desired results. This is where Oscar’s Handyman &amp; Pest Control Services’ come in.\r\n\r\nOscar’s pest control personnel are expert exterminators, proficient in pest control for common residential and commercial building pests, such as cockroaches, spiders, ants, bees, mosquitoes, flies, termites, bugs, and rodents.\r\n\r\nOur Pest Control services begin with initial survey and assessment of infestation and further lead to choosing the most effective pest control options from our range of pest control services, including general pest management, termite treatment, and bed bugs elimination.\r\nWe follow a holistic five point approach to pest control focused on education, sanitation and management, structural maintenance and repairs, biological and chemical control techniques, and limited pesticide application.\r\n\r\nWhat makes our pest control services special is our tailored approach to each case, on top of the flexible options we provide for damage control, especially to property and structures infested. We treat each case with utmost care by utilising safety protocols outlined by international &amp; Australian environmental pest control organisations.\r\n\r\nWe are committed to ensure total extermination of pests by making sure that all stages of the pest’s life is terminated. All our pest control methods are tested and proven to be effective. Moreover, our pest control services adhere to international &amp; Australian environmental safety standards to mitigate any health or environmental hazards brought about by the chemicals we use.\r\n<h3>So, contact or call 0457 985 003 if you’re looking for effective and efficient pest control services, let Oscar’s Pest Control Services give you a hand!</h3>', 'Pest Control Services', 'What makes our pest control services special is our tailored approach to each case, on top of the flexible options we provide for damage control, especially to property and structures infested. We treat each case with utmost care by utilising safety protocols outlined by international & Australian environmental pest control organisations.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'pest-control-services', '', '', '2015-11-16 12:20:58', '2015-11-16 12:20:58', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/?post_type=services&#038;p=39', 0, 'services', '', 0),
(40, 1, '2015-10-15 04:26:48', '2015-10-15 04:26:48', '', 'gallery04', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'gallery04', '', '', '2015-10-15 04:26:48', '2015-10-15 04:26:48', '', 39, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/gallery04.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(41, 1, '2015-10-15 04:28:22', '2015-10-15 04:28:22', '<h2>Are your walls looking a bit bland for the season? Want to start a painting project but don’t know where to start? Trying to salvage a botched do-it-yourself paint experiment? Let Handy Oscar get that done for you!</h2>\r\nWhile do-it-yourself paint jobs are often as disastrous as they’re cost effective, other professional painting services will offer you superficial painting services that will absolutely look cheap. The key to finding the right people to do the painting job for you is a careful balance of quality, efficiency, and cost.\r\n\r\nOur painting service personnel are professional trade painters with experience to boot. Our painters are experts in working with a wide range of painting materials, from varnish, primers, acrylics, vinyl, and emulsion to heavy masonry coatings, using standard brush and roller application or air spay. We also paint anything and everything, from smooth decorative surfaces, rough finishing with pebble dash buildings, factory claddings, food safety spaces, and commercial PVC’s, both new and refurbished.\r\n\r\nOur painting services cater to diverse paint jobs, whether it be large or small buildings, single houses, commercial projects, or industrial factories. Our range of professional services include paint refurbishment, interior and exterior painting, texture coatings, colour matching, protective and waterproof coatings, and stain blocking.\r\n\r\nOur painting services always begin with site assessment and colour selection and proceed to brand recommendation, making it a one stop service option that’s practical and cost-effective.\r\nWhat sets us apart is our keen attention to surface preparation, coupled with superior paint application and, of course, resilient finish. We are also committed to efficiently, doing the job by minimizing on site contact, especially for commercial spaces. We offer flexible hours to suit our clients’ demands, without compromising end results or deadlines. We also adhere to international safety and quality assurance standards, while ensuing environmental compliance.\r\n<h3>So, if you’re looking for professional painting service for your painting needs, let Handy Oscar give you a hand! Contact or Call 0457 895 033 Now!</h3>', 'Painting Services', 'Our painting services cater to diverse paint jobs, whether it be large or small buildings, single houses, commercial projects, or industrial factories. Our range of professional services include paint refurbishment, interior and exterior painting, texture coatings, colour matching, protective and waterproof coatings, and stain blocking.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'painting-services', '', '', '2015-11-16 12:04:37', '2015-11-16 12:04:37', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/?post_type=services&#038;p=41', 0, 'services', '', 0),
(42, 1, '2015-10-15 04:28:17', '2015-10-15 04:28:17', '', 'home03', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'home03', '', '', '2015-10-15 04:28:17', '2015-10-15 04:28:17', '', 41, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/home03.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(43, 1, '2015-10-15 04:30:06', '2015-10-15 04:30:06', '<h2>Looking at building a new storage for your kitchen? Considering to build a deck? Needing a hand for you door handles? No matter how easy or difficult the carpentry job you require, we can build it for you!</h2>\r\nCarpentry is one of the oldest professions. It essentially covers the cutting, forming, and installation of building materials for anything as simple as a rack to complex architectural buildings. While the most common materials used for this trade are natural wood, technological breakthroughs now allow carpenters to work on many other materials.\r\n\r\nWhile do-it-yourself kits and ready-to-assemble furniture are readily available in most local hardware, nothing can ever beat the workmanship guaranteed by professional tradesmen, not to mention the practicality in the cost and completion.\r\n\r\nOur carpentry service personnel are expert framers, trimmers, joiners, and furniture makers, who have been working in the trade skill for years. We can install anything from your doors, windows, interior trims, sidings, and insulation, to acoustic ceilings, metal framing, and wall partitions. We also offer custom built household and office furniture.\r\n\r\nOur carpentry services offer specialist design development, manufacture, and fixing services. Our work ranges from structural carpentry to specification joinery, and extend further to metalwork, vinyl, aluminium, and stainless materials. In the past, we have already installed structural timber framing, metal partitions, window sills, door hardware, and architraves.\r\nWhat sets us apart is our quality commitment and holistic approach to carpentry. We usually start with project assessment and site inspection where we come up with the pricing and project proposals.\r\n\r\nOur services are not simply limited to what’s commonly listed on carpentry services. We will be willing to customize carpentry solutions for your every need, complimented by flexible work hours aimed at reducing as much disturbance as possible.\r\n<h3>So contact us if you’re looking for practical and professional carpentry services, let Handyman’s Carpentry Services give you a hand!</h3>', 'Carpentry Services', 'Our carpentry service personnel are expert framers, trimmers, joiners, and furniture makers, who have been working in the trade skill for years. We can install anything from your doors, windows, interior trims, sidings, and insulation, to acoustic ceilings, metal framings, and wall partitions. We also offer custom built household and office furniture.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'carpentry-services', '', '', '2015-11-16 11:53:28', '2015-11-16 11:53:28', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/?post_type=services&#038;p=43', 0, 'services', '', 0),
(44, 1, '2015-10-15 04:30:02', '2015-10-15 04:30:02', '', 'home02', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'home02', '', '', '2015-10-15 04:30:02', '2015-10-15 04:30:02', '', 43, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/home02.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(45, 1, '2015-10-15 04:31:39', '2015-10-15 04:31:39', '<h2 style="text-align: center;">Needing some help with your door locks?\r\nCracked tiles that need replacement?\r\nOr does your entire home need some tending?\r\nHandy Oscar’s Repair and Renovation Service can absolutely help you!</h2>\r\nHome repairs and renovations can be as simple as replacing broken door locks to more technical tasks, such as retrofitting your household ventilations. Generally, repairs focus on fixing damages, while renovations are centered on improving outdated structures.\r\n\r\nWhile common fix-up and do-it-yourself materials are readily available in most hardware stores, some repair and renovation jobs are better left for the experts. Most repair and renovation jobs often require expertise in property construction, structural planning, water management, and sewage disposal, and even go as complex as design and financial administration.\r\n\r\nOur Repair and Renovation Services personnel include highly qualified and efficient specialists in trades such as carpentry, welding, and building construction, among others. These tradesmen are cross trained to ensure flexibility, especially in renovation projects.\r\nOur Repair and Renovation Services starts from assessment and effective planning, but we make sure to guide you through, step-by-step, for a guaranteed resolution to your repair and renovation needs.\r\n\r\nWe specialize in both residential and commercial repairs and construction. Some of our services include general buildings repairs, building renovations, emergency works, brick and mortar works, plastering &amp; gyprocking, demolition and roofing.\r\n\r\nWhat sets us apart are our trained professional tradesmen who delivers quality workmanship at very competitive pricing. We also ensure compliance to industry standards and existing legislative protocols to ensure safety and the integrity of our projects.\r\nMore importantly, we put you first. We offer flexible working hours that will best suit your schedule and even go beyond our normal services to take care of your repair and renovation requirements.\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">No matter how big or small your repair and renovation needs maybe, Handy Oscar is ready to give you a hand!</h3>', 'Repairs & Renovations', 'We specialize in both residential and commercial repairs and construction. Some of our services include general buildings repairs, building renovations, emergency works, brick and mortar works, plastering & gyprocking, demolition and roofing.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'repairs-renovations', '', '', '2015-11-16 11:44:41', '2015-11-16 11:44:41', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/?post_type=services&#038;p=45', 0, 'services', '', 0),
(46, 1, '2015-10-15 04:32:48', '2015-10-15 04:32:48', '<h2 style="text-align: center;">Trouble with your electrical wirings at home?\r\nOur expert electricians are here to help.</h2>\r\nElectrical services are generally focused in the installation of electrical components, maintenance, and repair. Some of the specializations under this category include residential, commercial, light industrial, and industrial and low-voltage wiring. Installation of control wirings and fire-alarm systems are also often done by specialist electricians.\r\n\r\nWhile simple light fixtures can easily be done with the aid of instructional guides, electrical wiring installation needs years of training especially in installing electrical systems, troubleshooting and maintenance, thus, these jobs are better done by certified electricians.\r\n\r\nOur electrical services personnel are highly trained professional electricians, with years of field experience. They possess expert skills in troubleshooting wiring problems, installing wiring in newly constructed and existing buildings, remodelling electrical systems, and service maintenance.\r\n\r\nOur electrical services include home theatre systems, data solutions, light fittings and installations, phone points, power points, safety inspections and reports, safety switches, smoke alarm installations, and inspection and certification of electrical appliances.\r\nSpecifically, we offer home maintenance and servicing, home theatre and multi room audio installations, new house wirings, electrical repairs and fault finding, lighting services, security alarm systems, and home automation and control.\r\n\r\nWhat sets our electrical services apart from our competition are our commitment to quality service, innovative solutions, and competitive prices. Our team will assess and determine your electrical requirements and offer the best solution that is tailored fit for your building requirements.\r\n\r\nWe are committed to offer you the best electrical services at par with industry standards, and with energy and cost effective options. We committed to your safety and satisfaction, so we make sure to comply with safety standards and protocols of existing legislations. We also offer flexible working hours to suit your convenience and minimize disturbance to your residential or commercial functions.\r\n<h3>So, contact us if you need expert electrical services, let handy Oscar give you a hand!</h3>', 'Electrical Services', 'Our electrical services include home theatre systems, data solutions, light fittings and installations, phone points, power points, safety inspections and reports, safety switches, smoke alarm installations, and inspection and certification of electrical appliances.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'electrical-services', '', '', '2015-11-16 11:30:34', '2015-11-16 11:30:34', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/?post_type=services&#038;p=46', 0, 'services', '', 0),
(47, 1, '2015-10-15 04:34:38', '2015-10-15 04:34:38', '<h2 style="text-align: center;">Broken pipes? Blocked drains? Leaking taps or shower?\r\nDon’t let these plumbing problems bother you!\r\nLet Handy Oscar do the job for you!</h2>\r\nPlumbing is an essential part of every household. Generally, it covers anything related to proper water supply for drinking, heating, and washing to waste removal and sewage systems.\r\nWhile plumbing are commonly pre-built along with most properties, the key to fool-proof plumbing system is professional installation and maintenance.\r\n\r\nHandy Oscar’s plumbing team is composed of highly trained professional plumbers with years of experience in the fields of plumbing, drainage systems, and sewage management. Their residential and industrial portfolios allow them to work with galvanized pipes, copper tubing, plastic pipes, and other plumbing fixtures.\r\n\r\nOur plumbing service cover gas, air-conditioning, heat pumps, ventilation systems, boilers, fire sprinkler systems, roofing, drainage, and even rainwater recycling. We are committed to ensure that all our plumbing services are specifically tailored to your property’s structural set-up and other plumbing requirements.\r\n\r\nWhat sets our services apart from our competition are our values, centered on professionalism, expertise, efficiency, and quality of every project, no matter how big or small. Thus, our services are guaranteed done by experts, with the most effective solutions, in an efficient manner and at par with industry standards.\r\n\r\nWe make sure that every job begins with on site assessment to tailor the best solution for your plumbing needs. We also value your time and space, so our flexible works hours are adjusted for your convenience. Our team are cross-trained in every technicality of planning, so you get one person to handle all the possible demands of your plumbing needs.\r\nWe don’t only offer you the best service but also the most cost-effective solutions, with our proven competitive rates. Handyman is compliant to plumbing protocols and safety standards laid out by international plumbing organizations, our way of assuring you that every job is done right!\r\n<h3>So, contact or call 0457 985 003 if you have any plumbing need, let Handy Oscar give you a hand!</h3>', 'Plumbing Services', 'Our plumbing service cover gas, air-conditioning, heat pumps, ventilation systems, boilers, fire sprinkler systems, roofing, drainage, and even rainwater recycling. We are committed to ensure that all our plumbing services are specifically tailored to your property’s structural set-up and other plumbing requirements.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'plumbing-services', '', '', '2015-11-16 11:24:19', '2015-11-16 11:24:19', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/?post_type=services&#038;p=47', 0, 'services', '', 0),
