(58, 1, '2015-11-16 12:54:29', '2015-11-16 12:54:29', 'Are you planning to renovate your home this season? Are you constantly plagued by recurring design issues? Thinking of adding a new furniture for your interiors? How about a new paintjob for the holiday? Passionate about household fix-ups and do-it-yourself projects but don’t have the time and patience? Worry no more! As they say, some jobs are better left for the experts.\n\nWe are a collective of passionate people, skilled at a wide range of trade handiworks for your every home requirement. We specialize in wide variety of exterior and interior repairs and maintenance works from the complicated task of plumbing to as simple as changing your electrical light fixtures. No matter how big or small the job is, we’ll gladly take care of it for you!\n\nOur personnel are cross-trained experts in trade skills such as electronics, plumbing, masonry, metal and wood works, carpentry, and general maintenance and repair works. We guarantee that the quality of our outputs are always at par with industry standards, or even better.\n\nOur growing range of handyman services currently includes fabrication and welding services, flooring services, pest control services, painting services, carpentry services repairs and renovations, electrical services, plumbing services, and granny flats conversions and building.\nWe cater to all industrial, commercial, and residential needs throughout the region, with prices depending on the complexity of the work required. What sets us apart from the rest of our competitors are our custom assessment and proficient quotation, strictly tailored to your needs and demands. Our team of expert assessors will gladly help you with the initial assessment and free estimates. All it takes is one quick survey!\nWe is committed to provide you with best solutions, quality jobs, and efficient services for all your household needs, without breaking the bank. Let our growing number of highly satisfied customers be a testament to our work.\nHandyoscar knows how to do the job right! That’s a commitment, not just a promise. So, talk to us today, and let Handyman do the job for you!\nOscar’s Handyman &amp; Pest Control Services\nABN: 52 903 464 015\nLicence: 15 101 893 001', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-11-16 12:54:29', '2015-11-16 12:54:29', '', 5, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/5-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(59, 1, '2015-10-16 03:48:15', '2015-10-16 03:48:15', 'Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry''s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.\r\n\r\nContrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia, looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur, from a Lorem Ipsum passage, and going through the cites of the word in classical literature, discovered the undoubtable source. Lorem Ipsum comes from sections 1.10.32 and 1.10.33 of "de Finibus Bonorum et Malorum" (The Extremes of Good and Evil) by Cicero, written in 45 BC. This book is a treatise on the theory of ethics, very popular during the Renaissance. The first line of Lorem Ipsum, "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet..", comes from a line in section 1.10.32.\r\n\r\nIt is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout. The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution of letters, as opposed to using ''Content here, content here'', making it look like readable English. Many desktop publishing packages and web page editors now use Lorem Ipsum as their default model text, and a search for ''lorem ipsum'' will uncover many web sites still in their infancy. Various versions have evolved over the years, sometimes by accident, sometimes on purpose (injected humour and the like).\r\n\r\nThere are many variations of passages of Lorem Ipsum available, but the majority have suffered alteration in some form, by injected humour, or randomised words which don''t look even slightly believable. If you are going to use a passage of Lorem Ipsum, you need to be sure there isn''t anything embarrassing hidden in the middle of text. All the Lorem Ipsum generators on the Internet tend to repeat predefined chunks as necessary, making this the first true generator on the Internet. It uses a dictionary of over 200 Latin words, combined with a handful of model sentence structures, to generate Lorem Ipsum which looks reasonable. The generated Lorem Ipsum is therefore always free from repetition, injected humour, or non-characteristic words etc.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-10-16 03:48:15', '2015-10-16 03:48:15', '', 5, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/5-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(61, 1, '2015-10-16 04:42:40', '2015-10-16 04:42:40', '', 'Services', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'services', '', '', '2015-10-16 04:44:27', '2015-10-16 04:44:27', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/?post_type=wck-meta-box&#038;p=61', 0, 'wck-meta-box', '', 0),
(62, 1, '2016-07-12 09:46:11', '2016-07-12 09:46:11', '<h2>Want to build a robust iron gate for your fortress or just a simple fixing of loose structural parts? Our fabrication and welding services is the right choice for you!</h2>\nFabrication and welding are twin services that deal with metal works. The construction of metal structures such as gates, railings, or metal pipes usually comes in three folds: cutting, bending, and assembling processes.\n\nThese processes are often complicated, not to mention dangerous, so it’s not recommended for the technically-challenged and the faint-hearted. It also requires industry grade equipment that are usually not available in your neighbourhood do-it-yourself hardware.\n\nOur fabrication and welding services personnel are qualified &amp; experts in their fields and geared with all the right equipment for various metal works.\n\nOur fabrication and wielding services include material consultation and sourcing, structure designing and engineering, metal preparation and assembly, and project installation. It’s basically a one stop service that offers additional value and convenience for your metal needs.\nWe can work with different types of metals including, but not limited to wrought iron, brass, aluminium, and cast iron. From the complicated custom fabrication and joining multi-material structures, to simple repair of existing wields or joining plumbing pipes, Handy Oscar can give you a hand.\n\nWhen looking for a fabricator or welder, it is important to make sure that they have sufficient experience on the kind of job required, especially with the materials you prefer. There are strict rules on these types of services and require stringent protocols, assessments, and certifications. Other requirements include safety protective equipment and industry-standard tools.\n\nOur fabricators and welders are trained in compliance to these requirements. Our fabricators are equipped with years of experience working on different variety of materials and installation complexities, while our welders strictly adhere to international &amp; Australia Welding Procedure Specification (WPS) and Welder Certifications.\n<h3>So, contact or call 0457 895 033 if you’re looking for Fabrication and Welding services, let Handy Oscar give you a hand!</h3>', 'Fabrication & Welding Services', 'Our fabrication and wielding services include material consultation and sourcing, structure designing and engineering, metal preparation and assembly, and project installation. It’s basically a one stop service that offers additional value and convenience for your metal needs.\nWe can work with different types of metals including, but not limited to wrought iron, brass, aluminium, and cast iron', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '35-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-07-12 09:46:11', '2016-07-12 09:46:11', '', 35, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/35-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
