(72, 1, '2015-10-17 02:33:19', '2015-10-17 02:33:19', '', 'Sandro Capozzi', 'The water was leaking thru the ceiling, I thought was a big job, Ls Handyman Services inspect my roof, Luca replace three tiles, clean up the gutters and install a leaves guard. Since then I have used him several times … ', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sandro-capozzi', '', '', '2015-10-17 02:33:19', '2015-10-17 02:33:19', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/?post_type=testimonials&#038;p=72', 0, 'testimonials', '', 0),
