(90, 1, '2015-11-16 11:58:08', '2015-11-16 11:58:08', '<h2>Are your walls looking a bit bland for the season? Want to start a painting project but don’t know where to start? Trying to salvage a botched do-it-yourself paint experiment? Let Handy Oscar get that done for you!</h2>\nWhile do-it-yourself paint jobs are often as disastrous as they’re cost effective, other professional painting services will offer you superficial painting services that will absolutely look cheap. The key to finding the right people to do the painting job for you is a careful balance of quality, efficiency, and cost.\n\nOur painting service personnel are professional trade painters with experience to boot. Our painters are experts in working with a wide range of painting materials, from varnish, primers, acrylics, vinyl, and emulsion to heavy masonry coatings, using standard brush and roller application or air spay. We also paint anything and everything, from smooth decorative surfaces, rough finishing with pebble dash buildings, factory claddings, food safety spaces, and commercial PVC’s, both new and refurbished.\n\nOur painting services cater to diverse paint jobs, whether it be large or small buildings, single houses, commercial projects, or industrial factories. Our range of professional services include paint refurbishment, interior and exterior painting, texture coatings, colour matching, protective and waterproof coatings, and stain blocking.\n\nOur painting services always begin with site assessment and colour selection and proceed to brand recommendation, making it a one stop service option that’s practical and cost-effective.\nWhat sets us apart is our keen attention to surface preparation, coupled with superior paint application and, of course, resilient finish. We are also committed to efficiently, doing the job by minimizing on site contact, especially for commercial spaces. We offer flexible hours to suit our clients’ demands, without compromising end results or deadlines. We also adhere to international safety and quality assurance standards, while ensuing environmental compliance.\n<h3>So, if you’re looking for professional painting service for your painting needs, let Handy Oscar give you a hand! Contact or Call 0457 895 033 Now!</h3>', 'Painting Services', 'Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry''s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '41-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-11-16 11:58:08', '2015-11-16 11:58:08', '', 41, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/41-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(91, 1, '2015-11-16 11:49:28', '2015-11-16 11:49:28', 'Looking at building a new storage for your kitchen? Considering to build a deck? Needing a hand for you door handles? No matter how easy or difficult the carpentry job you require, we can build it for you!\n\nCarpentry is one of the oldest professions. It essentially covers the cutting, forming, and installation of building materials for anything as simple as a rack to complex architectural buildings. While the most common materials used for this trade are natural wood, technological breakthroughs now allow carpenters to work on many other materials.\n\nWhile do-it-yourself kits and ready-to-assemble furniture are readily available in most local hardware, nothing can ever beat the workmanship guaranteed by professional tradesmen, not to mention the practicality in the cost and completion.\n\nOur carpentry service personnel are expert framers, trimmers, joiners, and furniture makers, who have been working in the trade skill for years. We can install anything from your doors, windows, interior trims, sidings, and insulation, to acoustic ceilings, metal framings, and wall partitions. We also offer custom built household and office furniture.\n\nOur carpentry services offer specialist design development, manufacture, and fixing services. Our work ranges from structural carpentry to specification joinery, and extend further to metalwork, vinyl, aluminum, and stainless materials. In the past, we have already installed structural timber framings, metal partitions, window sills, door hardware, and architraves.\nWhat sets us apart is our quality commitment and holistic approach to carpentry. We usually start with project assessment and site inspection where we come up with the pricing and project proposals. Our services are not simply limited to what’s commonly listed on carpentry services. We will be willing to customize carpentry solutions for your every need, complimented by flexible work hours aimed at reducing as much disturbance as possible.\nSo contact us if you’re looking for practical and professional carpentry services, let Handyman’s Carpentry Services give you a hand!', 'Carpentry Services', 'Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry''s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '43-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-11-16 11:49:28', '2015-11-16 11:49:28', '', 43, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/43-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(92, 1, '2015-11-16 11:39:53', '2015-11-16 11:39:53', '<h2 style="text-align: center;">Needing some help with your door locks?\nCracked tiles that need replacement?\nOr does your entire home need some tending?\nHandy Oscar’s Repair and Renovation Service can absolutely help you!</h2>\nHome repairs and renovations can be as simple as replacing broken door locks to more technical tasks, such as retrofitting your household ventilations. Generally, repairs focus on fixing damages, while renovations are centered on improving outdated structures.\n\nWhile common fix-up and do-it-yourself materials are readily available in most hardware stores, some repair and renovation jobs are better left for the experts. Most repair and renovation jobs often require expertise in property construction, structural planning, water management, and sewage disposal, and even go as complex as design and financial administration.\n\nOur Repair and Renovation Services personnel include highly qualified and efficient specialists in trades such as carpentry, welding, and building construction, among others. These tradesmen are cross trained to ensure flexibility, especially in renovation projects.\nOur Repair and Renovation Services starts from assessment and effective planning, but we make sure to guide you through, step-by-step, for a guaranteed resolution to your repair and renovation needs.\n\nWe specialize in both residential and commercial repairs and construction. Some of our services include general buildings repairs, building renovations, emergency works, brick and mortar works, plastering, gyprocking, demolition and roofing.\n\nWhat sets us apart are our trained professional tradesmen who delivers quality workmanship at very competitive pricing. We also ensure compliance to industry standards and existing legislative protocols to ensure safety and the integrity of our projects.\nMore importantly, we put you first. We offer flexible working hours that will best suit your schedule and even go beyond our normal services to take care of your repair and renovation requirements.\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">No matter how big or small your repair and renovation needs maybe, Handy Oscar is ready to give you a hand!</h3>', 'Repairs & Renovations', 'Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry''s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '45-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-11-16 11:39:53', '2015-11-16 11:39:53', '', 45, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/45-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(94, 1, '2015-10-26 00:25:42', '2015-10-26 00:25:42', 'Granny flats were generally intended to accommodate elderly or differently-abled members of the family for health and practicality benefits. However, over the course of time, it has become a popular property add on, favoured for its multi-use functionality.\r\n\r\nThe duality of granny flats make it a very marketable quality of any property for real property investors and developers.\r\n\r\nGranny flats are now being used as guest rooms and audio-visual hubs, complete with the prerequisite amenities like ling-room, bedroom, bathroom, and kitchen. Some of the common versions of granny flats are garage apartments, basement suites, single-attached or detached dwellings, and garden suites.\r\n\r\nWhile do-it-yourself options are now popular, building granny flats can be laborious and expensive. We offer practical, cost-effective, and efficient solutions for building your ideal granny flats whether it is for extra space or income.\r\n\r\nWe have highly trained, professional tradesmen, with expertise in fabrication and welding, carpentry, construction, electrical services &amp; plumbing. Expect a team of cross-trained experts to guide and help you assess, estimate, recommend, and build everything you’ll need in the granny flat.\r\n\r\nWe offer both granny flat conversions and pre-fabricated models and other customizable solutions for any of your granny flat needs. We can help you from brainstorming the design, choosing the materials, to building everything up, all with one streamlined approach.\r\nOur builders and project managers can offer you a wide range of design options from the facade, roofing, windows, kitchens, bathrooms, and floorings, and even help you with appliances and fixtures.\r\n\r\nWe pride ourselves with our innovative and industry standard solutions, geared to provide quality products, efficient service, all at very competitive prices. We also offer flexible working hours to suit your convenience.\r\nWe are more than just your average builders. We promise to make the process of delivering your needs beyond your expectations. Ours granny flat services are easy, efficient, and economic.\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">Considering building a granny flat?\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">Then <a style="color: #ff0000;" href="http://localhost/wp-ultra/contacts-us/">contact</a> or call 0457 895 033!</span>\r\nLet Handy Oscar give you a hand!</h3>', 'Granny Flats Conversions & Building', 'We offer both granny flat conversions and pre-fabricated models and other customizable solutions for any of your granny flat needs. We can help you from brainstorming the design, choosing the materials, to building everything up, all with one streamlined approach.\r\nOur builders and project managers can offer you a wide range of design options from the facade, roofing, windows, kitchens, bathrooms, and floorings, and even help you with appliances and fixtures.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'granny-flats-conversions-building', '', '', '2015-11-16 11:00:32', '2015-11-16 11:00:32', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp-ultra/?post_type=services&#038;p=94', 0, 'services', '', 0),
